thread.title: Axel
thread.title_full: Nengun Performance について 投稿者 Axel

author: Axel
title: Axel
text:
I recently ordered some Monster Sport parts for my car.
I could have bought them directly (and slightly cheaper) from Monster Sport, but I found the on-line shopping process, and the price combined with the shipping costs a lot better at Nengun Performance.
Status updates concerning my order were very much appreciated.
The item was well packaged and shipping times were very good.
Highly recommended!
